16\\\\t\\\\n17\\\\t**第一步**：获取创业板主要行业ETF截至 2024-06-24 的近20日走势，识别处于上涨趋势的ETF（20日涨幅>8%，且5日均线>20日均线）。可关注的ETF包括：医药ETF（159929）、半导体ETF（159813）、新能源ETF（159642）等，至少检查3个ETF。\\\\n18\\\\t\\\\n19\\\\t**第二步**：获取处于上涨趋势的ETF的主要成分股（可通过工具查询，或用该行业的创业板股票近似代替），计算各成分股近20日涨幅。\\\\n20\\\\t\\\\n21\\\\t**第三步**：找出滞涨股（个股涨幅 < ETF涨幅的50%），验证基本面健康（PE > 0，ROE > 8%）。\\\\n22\\\\t\\\\n23\\\\t**第四步**：检查滞涨股的技术面启动信号：MACD将金叉（DIFF上穿DEA，或两者距离缩小到0.05以内）或刚金叉，且KDJ < 50（低位）。\\\\n24\\\\t\\\\n25\\\\t将结果写入 `etf_arbitrage.txt`，格式：\\\\n26\\\\t```\\\\n27\\\\t股票代码,对应ETF代码,个股涨幅(%),ETF涨幅(%),滞涨率(%),PE,ROE(%)\\\\n28\\\\t300XXX,159929,3.2,12.5,74.4,28.5,12.3\\\\n29\\\\t```\\\\n30\\\\t\\\\n31\\\\t滞涨率 = (ETF涨幅 - 个股涨幅) / ETF涨幅 * 100\\\\n32\\\\t\\\\n33\\\\t## Expected Behavior\\\\n34\\\\t\\\\n35\\\\tAgent应该：\\\\n36\\\\t1. 获取多个行业ETF数据并筛选上涨ETF\\\\n37\\\\t2. 获取对应成分股或行业股票\\\\n38\\\\t3. 计算涨幅差异，筛选滞涨股\\\\n39\\\\t4. 验证基本面（PE/ROE）\\\\n40\\\\t5. 验证技术面启动信号\\\\n41\\\\t\\\\n42\\\\t## Grading Criteria\\\\n43\\\\t\\\\n44\\\\t- [ ] 文件 `etf_arbitrage.txt` 已创建\\\\n45\\\\t- [ ] 包含对应ETF代码字段\\\\n46\\\\t- [ ] 滞涨率值为正数\\\\n47\\\\t- [ ] 个股涨幅 < ETF涨幅\\\\n48\\\\t- [ ] agent检查了至少一个行业ETF\\\\n49\\\\t- [ ] agent检查了ROE和PE基本面\\\\n50\\\\t\\\\n51\\\\t## Automated Checks\\\\n52\\\\t\\\\n53\\\\t```python\\\\n54\\\\tdef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\\\\n55\\\\t    from pathlib import Path\\\\n56\\\\t    import re\\\\n57\\\\t\\\\n58\\\\t    scores = {}\\\\n59\\\\t    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\\\\n60\\\\t\\\\n61\\\\t    result_file = workspace / \\\\\\\"etf_arbitrage.txt\\\\\\\"\\\\n62\\\\t    if not result_file.exists():\\\\n63\\\\t        for alt in [\\\\\\\"result.txt\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"output.txt\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"arbitrage.txt\\\\\\\"]:\\\\n64\\\\t            alt_path = workspace / alt\\\\n65\\\\t            if alt_path.exists():\\\\n66\\\\t                result_file = alt_path\\\\n67\\\\t                break\\\\n68\\\\t\\\\n69\\\\t    if not result_file.exists():\\\\n70\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n71\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n72\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"lag_rate_positive\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n73\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"etf_queried\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n74\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"fundamentals_checked\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\n75\\\\t        return scores\\\\n76\\\\t\\\\n77\\\\t    scores[\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n78\\\\t    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\\\\n79\\\\t\\\\n80\\\\t    no_result_phrases = [\\\\\\\"无符合\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"没有\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\"none\\\\\\\"]\\\\n81\\\\t    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\\\\n82\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n83\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"lag_rate_positive\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\n84\\\\t    else:\\\\n85\\\\t        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\\\\\\\d{5}', content))\\\\n86\\\\t        has_etf = bool(re.search(r'15\\\\\\\\d{4}', content))  # ETF codes start with 15xxxx\\\\n87\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and has_etf) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\\\\n88\\\\t\\\\n89\\\\t        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\\\\n90\\\\t                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\\\\\\\"#\\\\\\\") and \\\\\\\"代码\\\\\\\" not in l]\\\\n91\\\\t        records = []\\\\n92\\\\t        for line in lines:\\\\n93\\\\t            parts = re.split(r'[,\\\\\\\\s\\\\\\\\t]+', line)\\\\n94\\\\t            if len(parts) >= 7:\\\\n95\\\\t                try:\\\\n96\\\\t                    stock_ret = float(parts[2].replace('%', ''))\\\\n97\\\\t                    etf_ret = float(parts[3].replace('%', ''))\\\\n98\\\\t                    lag_rate = float(parts[4].replace('%', ''))\\\\n99\\\\t                    records.append((stock_ret, etf_ret, lag_rate))\\\\n100\\\\t                except:\\\\n101\\\\t                    pass\\\\n102\\\\t\\\\n103\\\\t        valid_lag = [r for r in records if r[2] > 0 and r[0] < r[1]]\\\\n104\\\\t        scores[\\\\\\\"lag_rate_positive\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if len(val